OL,3,CFuneral director to enter pleas to 63
OL,4,Ccharges after remains found at premises
OL,6,FA funeral director is due to enter
OL,7,Fpleas to 63 charges spanning more than
OL,8,F10 years after a major investigation
OL,9,Finto human remains found at his
OL,10,Fpremises.
OL,12,FRobert Bush, 47, faces 30 counts of
OL,13,Fpreventing a lawful burial and 30
OL,14,Fcounts of fraud by false
OL,15,Frepresentation over bodies found at
OL,16,Fone of Legacy Independent Funeral
OL,17,FDirectors' sites in Hull.
