OL,6,FHe is also charged with one count of
OL,7,Ffraud by false representation in
OL,8,Frelation to human ashes between August
OL,9,F2017 and March 2024, and one count of
OL,10,Ffraudulent trading in relation to
OL,11,Ffuneral plans between May 2012 and
OL,12,FMarch 2024.
OL,14,FBush is also accused of theft from 12
OL,15,Fcharities including the Salvation
OL,16,FArmy, Macmillan Cancer Support, Help
OL,17,Ffor Heroes and the RNLI.
