OL,3,CFuneral director to enter pleas to 63
OL,4,Ccharges after remains found at premises
OL,6,FThe defendant, formerly of Kirk Ella,
OL,7,FEast Yorkshire, but now of Otley, West
OL,8,FYorkshire, is due to appear at Hull
OL,9,FCrown Court for a plea hearing on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FHumberside Police launched a probe
OL,13,Finto the funeral home after a report
OL,14,Fof "concern for care of the deceased"
OL,15,Fin March last year.
OL,17,FA month after the investigation
OL,18,Fstarted the force said it had received
OL,19,Fmore than 2,000 calls on a dedicated
OL,20,Fphone line from families concerned
OL,21,Fabout their loved ones' ashes.
